---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SectionDivider from "../components/SectionDivider.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Mindy | Divine Health Homeopathy"
  description="Meet Mindy Wallent, founder of Divine Health Homeopathy, and learn how her experience as a nurse, mother, and seeker of Truth led her to classical homeopathy."
>
  <main>

    <!-- Page introduction -->
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-hero-inner">

        <div class="about-hero-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">Meet Mindy</p>

          <h1>
            Nurse. Mother.<br />
            Student of Classical Homeopathy.
          </h1>

          <div class="divider-wrap">
            <SectionDivider />
          </div>

          <p class="hero-intro">
            Before she was a homeopath, Mindy was a wife, a mother of four
            beautiful children, and a nurse. Those roles shaped not only who she
            is, but also the practitioner she has become.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="portrait-frame">
          <img
            src="/images/mindy-headshot.jpg"
            alt="Mindy Wallent, founder of Divine Health Homeopathy"
            class="portrait"
          />
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Truth and nursing -->
    <section class="story-section story-light">
      <div class="story-container story-narrow">

        <p class="eyebrow centered">A Search for Truth</p>

        <h2>
          A lifelong desire to understand health and healing.
        </h2>

        <SectionDivider />

        <div class="story-copy">
          <p>
            From an early age, Mindy was driven by a desire to understand how
            the human body was designed to heal. She has always been drawn to
            asking questions, looking beyond the obvious, and searching for
            Truth wherever it could be found.
          </p>

          <p>
            That curiosity led her into nursing shortly after high school
            through Henry Ford College in Michigan, where she began a career
            devoted to caring for others.
          </p>

          <p>
            During her fourteen years as a nurse, Mindy gained a deep
            appreciation for modern medicine and the important role it plays in
            acute and emergency care. At the same time, she began to recognize
            something that would profoundly shape her life&rsquo;s work:
            health is not simply the absence of disease.
          </p>

          <p>
            She came to believe that we can either invest in caring for our
            bodies, minds, and spirits throughout life, or eventually pay the
            price through declining health.
          </p>
        </div>

        <blockquote>
          <p>
            After stepping away from nursing to raise her growing family, that
            belief became deeply personal.
          </p>
        </blockquote>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Son's first health challenge -->
    <section class="story-section story-parchment">
      <div class="story-container split-story">

        <div class="story-heading-column">
          <p class="eyebrow">A Mother&rsquo;s Search</p>

          <h2>
            Discovering a different way of understanding health.
          </h2>

          <div class="divider-left">
            <SectionDivider />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-copy">
          <p>
            In 2010, her one-year-old son suddenly developed severe breathing
            problems. Like many parents, Mindy searched for answers, determined
            to help her child regain his health.
          </p>

          <p>
            During that search, she discovered classical homeopathy. Under the
            care of a classical homeopath, her son improved dramatically,
            opening the door to an entirely new way of understanding health and
            healing.
          </p>

          <p>
            Several years later, their family faced another difficult
            challenge. The same son developed chronic hives that flared with
            nearly everything he ate. The rashes were often accompanied by
            swollen, painful joints and episodes of shortness of breath.
          </p>

          <p>
            By then, the family&rsquo;s original homeopath had retired,
            beginning another search for answers.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Searching again -->
    <section class="story-section story-light">
      <div class="story-container story-narrow">

        <p class="eyebrow centered">Searching Again</p>

        <h2>
          Temporary improvement was not the same as lasting change.
        </h2>

        <SectionDivider />

        <div class="story-copy">
          <p>
            Over the following years, they pursued many avenues of care,
            including alternative medicine, and found temporary improvement,
            but the problem continued to return.
          </p>

          <p>
            It wasn&rsquo;t until they found another classical homeopath&mdash;an
            Academy of Homeopathy Education graduate practicing individualized,
            one-remedy-at-a-time classical homeopathy&mdash;that lasting healing
            finally occurred.
          </p>

          <p>
            Today, he has been free of chronic hives for more than four years
            and enjoys the healthy, active life every parent hopes for their
            child.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Mindy's personal health story -->
    <section class="story-section story-navy">
      <div class="story-container split-story">

        <div class="story-heading-column">
          <p class="eyebrow">When Healing Became Personal</p>

          <h2>
            Mindy&rsquo;s own search for lasting answers.
          </h2>

          <div class="divider-left">
            <SectionDivider />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-copy light-copy">
          <p>
  Not long afterward, Mindy faced her own health challenges. After spending
  many hours working outdoors on their newly purchased home&mdash;property
  that had long been home to abundant wildlife, including deer&mdash;she
  discovered a distinctive bullseye rash on her arm. Although she never found
  a tick, the years that followed brought overwhelming fatigue, brain fog,
  forgetfulness, and the unsettling feeling that she was no longer herself.
</p>

          <p>
            With three young children&mdash;only two, three, and six years
            old&mdash;she often felt as though she had never recovered from the
            postpartum period.
          </p>

          <p>
            Once again, she searched for answers. While various therapies
            provided some improvement, it was individualized classical
            homeopathy that brought lasting change.
          </p>

          <p>
            As her own health steadily returned, she experienced a level of
            vitality she had not thought possible&mdash;including welcoming her
            fourth child at forty-one years of age.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Family's ongoing experience -->
    <section class="story-section story-parchment">
      <div class="story-container story-narrow">

        <p class="eyebrow centered">A New Approach to Health</p>

        <h2>
          Classical homeopathy became part of family life.
        </h2>

        <SectionDivider />

        <div class="story-copy">
          <p>
            Since establishing care with an Academy of Homeopathy Education
            graduate in 2022, classical homeopathy has become an integral part
            of her family&rsquo;s approach to health.
          </p>

          <p>
            Today, they continue to experience stronger overall wellness,
            greater resilience during acute illnesses, and lasting improvements
            that have transformed the way they think about healing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <blockquote>
          <p>
            Experiencing these profound changes firsthand sparked something
            deeper than curiosity. It became a calling.
          </p>
        </blockquote>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Education and calling -->
    <section class="story-section story-light">
      <div class="story-container split-story">

        <div class="story-heading-column">
          <p class="eyebrow">From Experience to Calling</p>

          <h2>
            Pursuing formal study in classical homeopathy.
          </h2>

          <div class="divider-left">
            <SectionDivider />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-copy">
          <p>
            Determined to fully understand the system of medicine that had so
            dramatically changed her family&rsquo;s life, Mindy began formal
            study in classical homeopathy.
          </p>

          <p>
            She has completed the didactic portion of her education through the
            Academy of Homeopathy Education and is currently completing her
            clinical internship.
          </p>

          <p>
            The search for Truth that first led Mindy into nursing continues to
            guide her today as she studies and practices classical
            homeopathy&mdash;always seeking to understand each person as an
            individual rather than simply treating a collection of symptoms.
          </p>

          <p>
            Today, Mindy serves as a supervised student practitioner through
            Homeopathy Help Network, working with clients under the guidance of
            experienced professional classical homeopaths.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Philosophy and CTA -->
    <section class="philosophy-section">
      <div class="philosophy-inner">

        <p class="eyebrow centered">Her Philosophy of Care</p>

        <h2>
          Every person&rsquo;s story deserves to be heard.
        </h2>

        <SectionDivider />

        <p class="philosophy-copy">
          Mindy brings together fourteen years of nursing experience with a
          deep respect for individualized classical homeopathy. She believes
          that every person&rsquo;s story is unique, every case deserves
          thoughtful attention, and healing is not about treating a
          diagnosis&mdash;it is about caring for the whole person.
        </p>

        <div class="about-actions">
          <Button href="/consultations" variant="gold">
            Learn About Consultations
          </Button>

          <Button
            href="https://homeopathyhelpnow.com/services/"
            target="_blank"
            variant="primary"
          >
            Schedule a Consultation
          </Button>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-hero {
    padding: 84px 40px 104px;

    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at top left,
        #fffdf8 0%,
        #f8f1e6 58%,
        #eee1ce 100%
      );
  }

  .about-hero-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;

    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 82px;
  }

  .about-hero-copy {
    max-width: 690px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 18px;

    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .centered {
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1,
  h2 {
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 28px;

    font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 6vw, 5.4rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 auto 27px;

    font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 4.8vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.06;
  }

  .divider-wrap,
  .divider-left {
    width: max-content;
  }

  .divider-wrap {
    margin-bottom: 31px;
  }

  .divider-left {
    margin-top: 29px;
  }

  .hero-intro {
    margin: 0;

    color: #40516a;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .portrait-frame {
    width: min(100%, 390px);
    justify-self: center;

    padding: 11px;

    background: rgba(255, 252, 246, 0.78);
    border: 1px solid #dfd0b7;
    border-radius: 38px;

    box-shadow:
      0 30px 72px rgba(16, 35, 63, 0.17);
  }

  .portrait {
    display: block;

    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;

    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;

    border-radius: 29px;
  }

  .story-section {
    padding: 116px 40px;
  }

  .story-light {
    background: #fffdf9;
  }

  .story-parchment {
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at top,
        #fcf8f0 0%,
        #f4eadb 100%
      );
  }

  .story-navy {
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at top left,
        #183b64 0%,
        #102947 48%,
        #081526 100%
      );
  }

  .story-container {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-narrow {
    max-width: 900px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .split-story {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.82fr 1.18fr;
    gap: 86px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-heading-column {
    position: sticky;
    top: 145px;
  }

  .story-heading-column h2 {
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .story-copy {
    margin-top: 35px;

    color: #3f5068;
    font-size: 1.13rem;
    line-height: 1.92;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .split-story .story-copy {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .story-copy p {
    margin: 0 0 29px;
  }

  .story-copy p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .light-copy {
    color: rgba(255, 250, 240, 0.9);
  }

  .story-navy h2 {
    color: #fffaf0;
  }

  blockquote {
    max-width: 770px;
    margin: 54px auto 0;
    padding: 30px 38px;

    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.34);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 0 20px 20px 0;

    box-shadow:
      0 14px 38px rgba(16, 35, 63, 0.06);
  }

  blockquote p {
    margin: 0;

    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 1.34rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.67;
  }

  .philosophy-section {
    padding: 124px 40px;

    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at top,
        #fffaf3 0%,
        #f3e7d5 100%
      );

    text-align: center;
  }

  .philosophy-inner {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .philosophy-copy {
    margin: 34px auto 0;

    color: #40516a;
    font-size: 1.22rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .about-actions {
    margin-top: 47px;

    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-hero {
      padding: 68px 24px 86px;
    }

    .about-hero-inner,
    .split-story {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 54px;
    }

    .about-hero-copy {
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .divider-wrap {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .portrait-frame {
      width: min(100%, 410px);
    }

    .story-section {
      padding: 92px 24px;
    }

    .story-heading-column {
      position: static;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .divider-left {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .split-story .story-copy {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .about-hero {
      padding: 58px 20px 74px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3.15rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2.6rem;
    }

    .hero-intro,
    .philosophy-copy {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
    }

    .story-section {
      padding: 76px 20px;
    }

    .story-copy {
      margin-top: 30px;

      font-size: 1.04rem;
      line-height: 1.84;
    }

    .story-copy p {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    blockquote {
      margin-top: 44px;
      padding: 25px 26px;
    }

    blockquote p {
      font-size: 1.16rem;
    }

    .philosophy-section {
      padding: 88px 20px;
    }

    .about-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
  }
</style>